response.overview: Carl Fredricksen spent his entire life dreaming of exploring the globe and experiencing life to its fullest. But at age 78, life seems to have passed him by, until a twist of fate (and a persistent 8-year old Wilderness Explorer named Russell) gives him a new lease on life.
response.tagline: The greatest adventure is just getting back home.
response.title: Up

titles.title: Up, Una aventura de altura Pixar
